  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Korabbian Spice is an extremely rare crystallized white
  spice is valued for its unique medicinal properties. Under special circum=
stances
  deposits of Korabbian spice will spontaneously accumulate on the walls of
  rocky canyons.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>The exact process that forms Korabbian spice has never =
been
  precisely identified. But it is theorized that the spice is created by a
  chemical reaction between certain types of rocks and the harsh, hot winds
  that sometimes gust through the canyons.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>It dramatically increases mental sharpness, allowing a
  being to perform incredible intellectual feats. Any colony supplied with
  Korabbian spice thus receives a 30% development bonus, over and above any
  other bonus. Once discovered, every effort should be made to control the
  trade of this highly valuable resource.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Korabbian spice is found exclusively on Desert worlds.<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Occurrence: extremely rare<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Type: Luxury Resource</span><span lang=3DEN-GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
